text: Poliaenus obscurus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Fall in 1910.BioLib.cz - Poliaenus obscurus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==Subspecies== * Poliaenus obscurus albidus Linsley, 1933 * Poliaenus obscurus obscurus (Fall, 1910) * Poliaenus obscurus ponderosae Linsley, 1935 * Poliaenus obscurus schaefferi Linsley, 1933 ==References== Category:Pogonocherini Category:Beetles described in 1910
